{"tid":1565084,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［黨鐵跨欄選拔賽］ 出閘位置跳入去，入閘位置跳出來","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T12:52:54.000Z","uid":7547,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1dedc234a8976ba09d3aa6948563d361559f3d","tid":1565084,"uid":7547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"首先喺假設冇便衣狗/黨鐵狗<br />\n<br />\n此舉喺針對藍絲正義撚，如果你出閘位置跳出，啲藍絲本身順路嘅，就會吊住你尾搞事，本身時間成本=零。正所謂冇代價又可以玩嘢，做乜唔玩？<br />\n<br />\n但係你逆行線跳，藍絲本身出左閘/準備出閘，見你跳入去，佢如果吊你尾/搞事，要行返轉頭，會浪費佢嘅時間。藍絲咁窩囊，要付出嘅嘢點會做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申跳左兩次閘之後，去左逆行線閘位附近嘅欄杆跳"},{"pid":"66dc56b17edeaa5861b39d90777ac62195a3f95e","tid":1565084,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0be980500f59d5e79a8286099e9a0efb0a410170","tid":1565084,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" />